IN RE the MARRIAGE OF Douglas WHALEN, Jr. and Morgan Whalen Upon the Petition of Douglas Whalen, Jr., Petitioner-Appellee, And Concerning Morgan Whalen, Respondent-Appellant. No. 18-0573 Court of Appeals of Iowa. Filed April 3, 2019

DECISION WITHOUT PUBLISHED OPINION

See Iowa R. App. P. 6.904

Morgan Whalen appeals from the district court order granting Douglas Whalen's motion to reconsider provisions of the parties' dissolution decree. ORDER VACATED.

ORDER VACATED.
